sx.blah.discord.handle.audio

Interface IAudioProcessor

  • All Superinterfaces:
    IAudioProvider
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    DefaultProcessor, MultiProcessor, PauseableProcessor, VolumeProcessor

    public interface IAudioProcessor
extends IAudioProvider
    This represents an audio processor (something that manipulates raw audio data before it is sent to discord).

    • Method Detail

      • setProvider

        boolean setProvider(IAudioProvider provider)
        This sets the IAudioProvider this processor is wrapping and returns whether this processor is compatible with the provided provider instance.
        Parameters:
        provider - The provider to use. If a previous provider was wrapped, it should be replaced by this object.
        Returns:
        True if compatible, false if otherwise (in this case the processor will not be called to retrieve audio data.
